OL,3,CCompany fined #1.6m after 24-year-old
OL,4,Cman crushed to death
OL,6,FA company has been fined #1.6m after a
OL,7,F24-year-old man was crushed to death
OL,8,Fin Sussex.
OL,10,FJack Phillips lost his life on 8
OL,11,FAugust 2019 while working for Brand
OL,12,FEnergy and Infrastructure Services UK
OL,13,FLtd at South Cliff Tower in Eastbourne.
OL,15,FJack had been assisting while
OL,16,Ftemporary Mast Climber Work Platform
OL,17,Fsections were being lifted by a lorry-
OL,18,Fmounted crane.
