OL,3,CCompany fined #1.6m after 24-year-old
OL,4,Cman crushed to death
OL,6,FThe load fell on top of Jack when the
OL,7,Flifting sling which was attached to
OL,8,Fthe crane snapped.
OL,10,FHis parents say they are "no longer
OL,11,Fcomplete" following the loss of their
OL,12,F"happy-go-lucky" son.
OL,14,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,15,FSafety Executive (HSE) and Sussex
OL,16,FPolice found Brand Energy &
OL,17,FInfrastructure Services UK Ltd,
OL,18,Ftrading as Lyndon SGB, failed to
OL,19,Fproperly plan the lifting operation of
OL,20,Fthe work platform.
