OL,3,CCompany fined #1.6m after 24-year-old
OL,4,Cman crushed to death
OL,6,FThe company, a provider of temporary
OL,7,Faccess equipment, had "failed to
OL,8,Fidentify a requirement for safe
OL,9,Fexclusion zones".
OL,11,FThe investigation also found the
OL,12,Fcompany had failed to have a suitable
OL,13,Frobust system in place to ensure all
OL,14,Faccessories had been thoroughly
OL,15,Fexamined or disposed when expired.
OL,16,FThis resulted in out-of-date slings
OL,17,Fbeing used.
