OL,3,CCompany fined #1.6m after 24-year-old
OL,4,Cman crushed to death
OL,6,FJack's parents, Scot and Nichola, said
OL,7,Fin a statement: "How do you put into
OL,8,Fwords the utter devastation you feel.
OL,9,FOur child, our only son, is dead. Our
OL,10,Flife, our family's life has now
OL,11,Fchanged forever.
OL,13,F"We are no longer complete without
OL,14,FJack, we will never see our baby boy,
OL,15,Fthe boy we nurtured and helped grow
OL,16,Finto a young man, get married, raise a
OL,17,Ffamily, or grow old.
