OL,3,CCompany fined #1.6m after 24-year-old
OL,4,Cman crushed to death
OL,6,F"His sisters will never have the
OL,7,Fhonour of him being an uncle to their
OL,8,Fchildren. We will never have the
OL,9,Fhonour of seeing or meeting his
OL,10,Fchildren. Jack was a happy go lucky
OL,11,F"Jack the lad". Everyone who had the
OL,12,Fpleasure of meeting him, loved him."
OL,14,FBrand Energy and Infrastructure
OL,15,FServices UK Ltd, of Kingston Road,
OL,16,FLeatherhead, Surrey pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fbreaching Section 2(1) of the Health
OL,18,Fand Safety at Work etc. Act 1974.
