OL,6,F"Brand Energy and Infrastructure
OL,7,FServices UK Ltd failed in its duty of
OL,8,Fcare to all its operatives, including
OL,9,FJack, in the way it planned and
OL,10,Fimplemented the lifting operations and
OL,11,Fthe slack customs and practices it
OL,12,Fallowed to become part of the safety
OL,13,Fculture with regard to lifting."
